These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, pumpkin, nectarine, mango, cranberry, broccoli, grapes
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, turkish, dutch, pakistani, canadian, indonesian, nigerian
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating mango is not the indonesian##6
 3. the thai is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
 5. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 6. the thai is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 7. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating pumpkin and the turkish##7
 8. the turkish is on the left of the nigerian##1
 9. the pakistani is somewhere between the person eating cranberry and the dutch##7
10. the dutch is on the left or right of the thai##3
11. the canadian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
13. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
14. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
15. the person eating cranberry is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | nectarine    | watermelon    | pumpkin | broccoli | mango | cranberry    | grapes |
| Nationality   | canadian | thai | dutch  | indonesian   | pakistani    | turkish | nigerian |

