.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, asparagus, cranberry, garlic, tomato, raspberry, apple
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, fishing, cooking, sudoku, photography, magic-tricks, board-games
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person eating asparagus##7
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 6. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 7. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating asparagus##7
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
10. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person eating apple##6
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating garlic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | apple  | cranberry | raspberry | garlic | blueberry     | tomato | asparagus  |
| Hobby   | cooking | magic-tricks | fishing  | board-games  | photography | sudoku      | writing |

