 3. the fan of rock is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
 4. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
 5. the fan of trance is between the fan of folk and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 6. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the fan of pop and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
11. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of trance##6
13. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is baking##7
14. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
15. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
16. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of folk##6
17. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
18. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
19. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
