 2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
 5. the person who's sport is shiping is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person driving the tram##7
 8. the person who's sport is shiping is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
10. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is cycling##7
12. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
13. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
14. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
16. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
17. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the bike##2
18. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person driving the train##6
